/ ----- 'spots/search'で使用中 -----
h4.mt-3 スポット一覧
.flower-spots
  - @spots.each do |spot|
    .card.my-5
      = link_to spot_path(spot.id), class: "flower-spot"
        .row.no-gutters.py-2
          .col-9.body
            h1
              = spot.name
            .address
              = spot.location
            .season
              = spot.time
            p.mt-2
              = spot.feature
          .col-3.pl-2
            = image_tag spot.image.to_s, class: "image"

/ 検索後のスポット表示見本
